# Project Chimera: The Multi-AI Post-Mortem (FINAL)

## 1. Executive Summary
This report summarizes a massive, multi-AI collaborative research arc into **Continual Learning (CL)**. We compared 13 versions of the **Chimera Reservoir** (Fixed Dynamics) against a parallel track of **Coherence-Gated Learning (CGL)**.

### The Macro-Conclusion:
**Structure > Randomness.** 
The FRC goal of "Stable Memory" is NOT achieved by fixed random liquids (Reservoirs), but by **Intelligent Gating Mechanisms** (CGL) that regulate when and how gradients are used.

